      <body>
         <div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
            <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit"><ab>በስመ፡ … ድርሳን፡ ዘደረሰ፡ አባ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ ኢጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ዘሀገረ፡ ሥሩግ፡ በእንተ፡ አብርሃም፡ አቡነ፡ አርከ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡</ab></div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="subscriptio explicit" xml:id="colophon"><ab>
               ወይረሲ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ማኅደሮ፡ ለአቡነ፡ አባ፡ ሰላማ፡ ጳጳስነ፡ ምስሌሆሙ፡ ደርገ፡ አሜን፨ 
               ለዝንቱ፡ ድርሳን፡ ዘአጽሐፎ፡ አቡነ፡ አባ፡
               ሰላማ፡ ጳጳስ፡ ርቱዓ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ እምዐረቢ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ዚአሁ፡ ለግዕዝ፤ ይተሉ፡ ዝየ፡ ተጽሕፎ፡ ዘይቤ፡ አባ፡
               አትናስዮስ። <note>quoted after <ref type="mss" corresp="ESgbi002">GBI-002</ref></note> <note>Subscriptio ascribing the translation
                  of the homily (from Arabic into Gǝʿǝz) to Metropolitan <persName ref="PRS8387SalamaI">ʾabbā Salāma</persName>;
                  besides, the authorship of the work is here attributed to <persName ref="PRS2209Athanasi">Athanasius</persName>
                  (Bishop of Alexandria from 328 to 373; cp. EAE I, 392)</note>
            </ab></div>
            
